{"tid":627601,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"色叔叔逼弱女坐八爪椅　當她母親面「通血氣」","createTime":"2018-04-13T06:27:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-13T06:49:44.000Z","uid":72009,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5865f6d69df9debb9ff8bbfd36be4d930bd0577c","tid":627601,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T06:27:08.000Z","msg":"被告陳男（50多歲）跟女友疑似智能略有不足，但都未經鑑定，陳有了女友還不滿足，前年6月13日晚上，藉故要幫忙母女打通血氣為由，騙女友帶女兒一起上摩鐵。要求被害人坐在高腳椅（俗稱八爪椅），強制性侵時，被害人喊痛一度將陳推開，媽媽也阻止，最後仍讓陳嫌得逞。<br />\n由於社工擔心被害人遭人引誘、脅迫性而懷孕，前年8月安排結紮手術時，意外追問出遭陳男性侵才報警。陳嫌辯稱，是被害人自願跟他發生性行為，而且媽媽也在旁觀看，否認性侵害。<br />\n但檢方調查，陳嫌坦承，事先問過被害人是否願意？被害人回說：「要問媽媽！」顯然陳已知她有智能障礙，加上知道他是媽媽男朋友，因心智缺陷而無法抗拒，最後因疼痛推拒，卻仍遭性侵，陳嫌明顯違背她的性自主權。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180413/1333795\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180413%2F1333795&d=95vaTXnWF%2BaQOTHEBviKWwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=412f6d36\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180413%2F1333795&h=77124e96\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180413/1333795</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 母女"},{"pid":"68ce0bf618f482b7d05e3bb0c64b4061f779cf45","tid":627601,"uid":44916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T06:29:15.000Z","msg":"咩呀，即係三個都係智力有問題?"},{"pid":"868effdfa68118407207e6c460da24b41246e0f4","tid":627601,"uid":55924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T06:48:30.000Z","msg":"個女幾歲 要結紮？"},{"pid":"2abee6cd16225c7fdb71138de8b58b04fd307d52","tid":627601,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T06:49:44.000Z","msg":"樓主泛民打手waiwaiwai平時扮正常<br />\n一到選舉就現形打擊本土<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/13/144939_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F13%2F144939_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=21d03f13&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}